Sector.Credits: Empty Quarter sector was designed by Marc W. Miller and appears in Atlas of the Imperium (GDW, 1984). It was refined by Jason "Flynn" Kemp and Alvin Plummer and appears in Stellar Reaches Magazine. Empty Quarter sector 1248 borders designed by Shane MacLean, Eric O'Dell and Michael Taylor and appears in 1248 Sourcebook 1: Out of Darkness(ComStar Media/Avenger Enterprises, 2006).
